Package: querychat
Title: Filter and Query Data Frames in 'shiny' Using an LLM Chat Interface
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joe", "Cheng", , "joe@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Adds an LLM-powered chatbot to your 'shiny' app, that can turn your
  users' natural language questions into SQL queries that run against your data,
  and return the result as a reactive dataframe. Use it to drive reactive
  calculations, visualizations, downloads, etc.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
